pport do you have?","type":"control_checkbox"},null,{"description":"","name":"howMany408","qid":"408","subLabel":"","text":"How many children\u002Fstep children do you have in total?","type":"control_dropdown"},{"description":"","name":"name409","qid":"409","text":"What are the reasons you are being referred for services?","type":"control_checkbox"},null,null,{"description":"","name":"toAssist412","qid":"412","text":"To assist in identity verification clients are asked to  secure a credit card on file. If you have active full health insurance you will not be charged.  Credit Card will be used for payment of non covered intake and therapy fees, missed appointments, co-payments, deductibles, or expedited requests for documentation. You will not be charged right now.","type":"control_stripe"},null,{"description":"","name":"primaryReferral","qid":"414","subLabel":"","text":"Primary referral source name","type":"control_textbox"},{"description":"","name":"primaryReferral415","qid":"415","subLabel":"","text":"Primary referral source email","type":"control_textbox"},null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,{"description":"","name":"email","qid":"438","subLabel":"","text":"Email","type":"control_email"},{"name":"submit","qid":"439","text":"Submit","type":"control_button"},null,null,null,null,null,null,{"description":"","name":"address446","qid":"446","text":"Address","type":"control_address"},{"description":"","name":"name","qid":"447","text":"Name","type":"control_fullname"},{"description":"","name":"pleaseSeek448","qid":"448","subLabel":"Call 911 and ask for the ambulance. As you are waiting for the ambulance, you may call National Suicide Prevention Lifeline at 1-800-273-8255 for extra support. Please don&#039;t act on suicidal feelings. This is a symptom of depression and help is available.","text":"Please seek immediate help.","type":"control_textbox"},null,null,null,null,null,null,{"description":"","